lyrics:
I was happy once upon time
And now I can't be no more
Because all the lights are going out tonight
Maybe one day I will find
A beautiful loving girl to be on my side
And then I won't blame no one else
God's looking for me in a dark street
My spirit is about that life
My dream life is about that girl
May I find her today or tomorrow
Today or tomorrow
Shall I find her
Today or tomorrow
Ye
style: Japanese Koto/ Female Singer/ drum and bass
